{
    "story_id": "",
    "story_name": "初阳！日出决战 桂影无情",
    "story_icon": "",
    "outline": {
        "title": [
            "剧情概要"
        ],
        "content": [
            "月读企图创造一个由龙掌权的亡者国度。\\n她残忍地笑称要杀死王子一行\\n并将其变为对自己唯命是从的士兵。\\n此时不动明王现身，救众人于危难之中。\\n解开束缚的王子一行将与月读交锋！"
        ]
    },
    "story_content": [
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "日出之国，\\n极东之地的始祖之龙伊邪那岐\\n与伊邪那美所创造的岛屿。\\n统治岛屿的，则是继承了\\n始祖之龙力量的天照和月读。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0059",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "然而天照和月读却出现了分歧。\\n天照渴望与人携手共进，\\n月读则认为应由龙来掌控世界。\\n于是，日出之国最初的战争就此爆发。\\n这便是“天地初战”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0060",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [],
            "speaker_name": "SYS",
            "context": "经历漫长的战争之后，\\n天照获得了胜利，\\n落败的月读被封印在昏暗的岩洞之中。\\n日出之国则在后来\\n成为了由人类统治的国度。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0061",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "但是在大约100年前，\\n月读却忽然从岩洞中消失……\\n是这样对吧，出云阁下？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0001",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "出云",
            "context": "是、是的……没错。\\n可她究竟又是如何从那\\n岩洞中脱身前往黄泉国的……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0002",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "呵呵呵……你们喜欢听故事啊？\\n很好，本宫也正想找人聊聊天呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0003",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "很久很久以前……\\n曾有一个男人到岩洞中\\n来寻找本宫。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0004",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "原来适逢乱世，\\n那男人为了自己的主君\\n而前来向本宫讨要不死之水。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0005",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "多么美好的忠臣佳话啊……\\n于是本宫便答应了他。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0006",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "不过作为交换条件……\\n本宫要他帮忙拿到“道反石”。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0007",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "然后你就用道反石\\n逃到了黄泉国是吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0008",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "哎呀，先别着急嘛。\\n就算是本宫，想进入黄泉国\\n也不是那么容易的事哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0009",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "打开黄泉国的大门需要\\n道反石和大量的气，\\n然而岩洞却阻断了气的流动。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0010",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "于是本宫便用上了“自己的气”。\\n也就是通过自尽的方法\\n打开了黄泉国之门。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0011",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "竟然以自身为活祭……\\n真是个彻头彻尾的疯子。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0012",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "疯子？不，本宫自然有自己的打算。\\n由于身死，本宫的气才得以\\n与黄泉国相融，最终融为一体。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0013",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "接下来便是暗中联系现世，\\n让骸众开启黄泉国之门。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0014",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "于是本宫终于在今夜……\\n重新降临于日出之国啦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0015",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100006_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "卢卡",
            "context": "呃……也就是说你不光摆脱了封印，\\n还得到了更加难缠的力量\\n卷土重来了是吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0016",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "呵呵呵……说话要小心哦？\\n你们这些人类今后\\n可都是要在本宫的统治之下呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0017",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "嚯……你是打算就此\\n率领骸众打倒幕府吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0018",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "没错。接下来本宫就要\\n用黄泉国的力量彻底破坏\\n天照那个家伙所统治的世界。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0019",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "让所有龙都对本宫俯首称臣，\\n再杀光人类……\\n创造一个亡者的国度。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0020",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "出云",
            "context": "什么！？亡者的……国度？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0021",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "没错。变成亡者其实挺不错的哦？\\n到时候就不会像你现在这样\\n因为恐惧而缩成一团了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0022",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "出云",
            "context": "！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0023",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "哎呀呀，看把这孩子吓得。\\n今后你就可以作为没有生命的人偶\\n在本宫的统治之下安稳度日了哦。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0024",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "哼，你的爱好还真是低俗。\\n我同样身为龙，听了都觉得恶心……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0025",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "嘻嘻嘻。如果你能看到本宫\\n眼中的世界，早晚都会懂的。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0026",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "日出之国是属于龙的大地。\\n这里的统治不需要会思考的人类。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0027",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "人类只需服从于女王，\\n按本宫的意愿行动便可……\\n这样才能消除纷争，还天下一个太平。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0028",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100010_05"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "穆穆",
            "context": "唉……果然是低级趣味。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0029",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "看来言语说明还不够呢……\\n那本宫就直接让你们体验一下吧。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0030",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "让本宫看看……\\n要用谁的命才好呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0031",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "命！？你、你想要干什么！？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0032",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "本宫刚才说了呀，\\n杀了你们做成没有生命的人偶。\\n然后再让人偶去杀人。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0033",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "你看起来似乎精通于魔法……\\n应该能成为一个杀人无数的\\n优秀士兵呢。呵呵呵。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0034",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100004_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "库菈乌",
            "context": "唔，住手……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0035",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110403_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "出云",
            "context": "库菈乌！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0036",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "哼。哈哈哈哈哈。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0037",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "实属……低俗。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0038",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "嚯……你说什么？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0039",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "老夫说你那所谓的建国之道实属低俗。\\n百姓才是国家的基石，\\n没有了百姓，谈何统治？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0040",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "在只有龙和亡者的世界里，\\n你要去统治谁呢？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0041",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "你那所谓的亡者国度——\\n真的能算是一个国家吗？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0042",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "呵呵……你是在挑衅本宫吗？\\n看来你是打算用这种方法拯救\\n自己的同胞呢……好一个动人的故事。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0043",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "但你还是别白费力气了。\\n反正你们全都要死在这里。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0044",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "不过呢……如果你是急着想要\\n赶快从死亡的恐惧中解脱的话……\\n本宫倒是可以遂了你的愿哦？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0045",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "那你尽管试试好了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0046",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "哦呵呵。你自命不凡的样子真可爱。\\n那就先请你来……踏上黄泉路吧？",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0047",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "？？？",
            "context": "休想！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0048",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "嗯……时机正好。\\n你办事果然还是让人放心，不动明王。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0049",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "不动明王",
            "context": "信玄大人……哪怕是一分一秒，\\n离开您都让妾身倍感孤独……\\n妾身这就为您松绑……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0050",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "原来是龙啊……\\n看来不小心让你们\\n成功拖延了时间呢。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0051",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210169_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "不动明王",
            "context": "你就是月读……\\n胆敢谋害信玄大人……\\n不可饶恕……",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0052",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110401_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "信玄",
            "context": "所有人都解开绳子了吗？\\n被收缴的武器都在那边，\\n迅速备战！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0053",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "100001_09"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "尤蒂尔",
            "context": "多谢。\\n既然已经得知月读的阴谋……\\n那就只有一战了！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0054",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "110402_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "幸村",
            "context": "交给我吧！\\n管她是龙还是什么妖魔鬼怪，\\n都由幸儿来消灭掉！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0055",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "你要消灭本宫？呵呵……哈哈哈！\\n真是白搭、白费劲、白日做梦！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0056",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "本宫原想将你们做成\\n外表完好的人偶，\\n看来现在只能打消这个念头了。",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0057",
            "book_image": ""
        },
        {
            "speaker_id": [
                "210028_01"
            ],
            "speaker_name": "月读",
            "context": "虽然多少会缺胳膊少腿……\\n本宫就让你们一起变为亡者吧！",
            "voice_line": "VO_CHR_EVENTSTORY_20441_04_0058",
            "book_image": ""
        }
    ]
}